name: 38/∞ • 2020 daily experiment (alternative v.)
description: experiment nº 38 (alternative version) from my series "•/∞" (2020), where I created images made with mobile apps. this one was made with mirrorlab's deform tool and animated with movee video app. original photography taken by vini cassol and edited on lightroom. taken: 2019, fundación proa, la boca, buenos aires - argentina, in front of dan flavin "Untitled (to Donna) 6, 1971".
